    //-------------------------------------------------------------------------
    // ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
    // This function is used to get write address phase information for 
    // outstanding write txn when write response with ID is received. It provides
    // write address phase info which can be used to relate response and address.
    // 
    // The info provided is correct only when ~valid~ output bit is set.
    // 
    // This function should be called after completion of write address phase for 
    // correct results.
    // 
